title: The One Where Ocean Does The Thizzle Face
description:
Lala and Ocean partied it up for Superbowl weekend complete with Thizzle Face! Ocean is definitely her mama’s daughter! And Lala and her brother Easton are both living their best lives! Easton’s going sex free for 2022 as he focuses on himself, but Lala’s ready to get it on! They talk about their high school days, what they’re looking for in a future partner, and how Easton feels about turning 30.
